701559f-a.title: Bronx: Outlook Avenue - Griswold Avenue
701559f-a.text:
Outlook Ave. (foreground, not seen), at Griwwold Ave. The view is
in a northerly direction towards Ampere Ave. and shows summer bungalows
lining the shore of Eastchester Bay.
July 17, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
